Si Shuhei Fujisawa (藤沢周平 Fujisawa Shūhei) (26 December 1927 - 26 January 1997) sakey ya Hapon ya managsulat. Tomeji Kosuge (小菅留治) so twan ngaran to. Onsobra ed 50 so libro so engalot; kaibab diya so full-length ran nobela san antekey ran istoria. Historical fiction so say focus na saray insulat to. Antes ya nanmaliw ya managsulat, nantrabaho ya sakey ya peryodista.

